747
00:50:11.809 --> 00:50:13.334
You're my first this week.

748
00:50:17.548 --> 00:50:20.211
Look. I have a big
decision to make.

749
00:50:20.284 --> 00:50:22.947
so if you don't mind.

750
00:50:23.787 --> 00:50:25.119
