asking for your advice.

755
00:50:38.903 --> 00:50:40.633
Well. I'm offering it anyway.

756
00:50:43.807 --> 00:50:45.833
The universe rewards courage.

757
00:50:47.478 --> 00:50:50.243
Mister. I just found out that my
mom's boyfriend murdered her

758
00:50:50.314 --> 00:50:53.807
30 years ago and got away with it.
so I don't need your fucking advice.

759
00:50:55.286 --> 00:50:56.806
How much do I owe you?

760
00:50:57.555 --> 00:50:58.454
What did you say?

761
00:50:58.522 --> 00:51:00.548
- How much do I owe you?
