772
00:51:51.675 --> 00:51:53.268
Because we had sex last night.

773
00:51:53.344 --> 00:51:54.505
I left it at a restaurant.

774
00:51:54.578 --> 00:51:55.855
And I thought we kind
of had a connection.

775
00:51:55.879 --> 00:51:58.110
I'm untraceable. My
own husband has no idea

776
00:51:58.182 --> 00:51:59.225
