- It wasn't hard.

777
00:51:59.249 --> 00:52:01.445
I have a tracking device
in my car. Wait. what?

778
00:52:01.518 --> 00:52:03.453
- You have a what?
- What did you just say?

779
00:52:03.520 --> 00:52:06.285
I think you heard me.

780
00:52:06.924 --> 00:52:08.290
Can you put the gun down?

781
00:52:18.335 --> 00:52:20.463
Well. I have to admit.
I feel kind of used.

782
00:52:21.338 --> 00:52:22.338
Sorry.

783
00:52:22.806 --> 00:52:24.638
You didn't seem
like the type to lie.

784
00:52:24.708 --> 00:52:27.872
I'm kind of a disaster
of a person. EJ.

785
00:52:28.278 --> 00:52:30.440
