wanted to kill him.

795
00:52:51.535 --> 00:52:53.561
- What?
- And they sided with him.

796
00:52:53.637 --> 00:52:57.199
Oh. my God.
Joanie. I'm so sorry.

797
00:52:58.876 --> 00:53:01.710
Yeah. guess I'll just
have to finish this myself.

798
00:53:02.946 --> 00:53:05.245
So. what. you're just gonna
go back and shoot him?

799
