807
00:53:21.598 --> 00:53:24.124
Because you
obviously don't care.

808
00:53:24.201 --> 00:53:26.397
You're clearly not
happy with your husband.

809
00:53:26.470 --> 00:53:27.981
If you were. you
wouldn't be here with me.

810
00:53:28.005 --> 00:53:30.565
I was alone here.
You just stalked me.

811
00:53:31.241 --> 00:53:35.110
My job is flying me to Vienna tomorrow
evening to speak at a conference.

812
00:53:35.579 --> 00:53:36.911
Why don't you come with me?

813
00:53:37.915 --> 00:53:38.915
And we can just...

814
00:53:39.950 --> 00:53:40.950
keep going.

815
00:53:46.190 --> 00:53:47.190
Sorry.

816
00:53:48.158 --> 00:53:49.558
I have to finish this.

817
00:53:52.496 --> 00:53:55.141
What good will it do to kill him? It's
not gonna bring your mother back.

818
00:53:55.165 --> 00:53:56.342
That's not what this is about.

819
00:53:56.366 --> 00:53:58.631
- He can't just get away with it.
- Joanie...

820
00:53:59.136 --> 00:54:00.604
Hey. hey. I like you.

821
00:54:01.105 --> 00:54:02.105
I really like you.

822
00:54:02.473 --> 00:54:03.668
You're fucking honest.

823
00:54:03.741 --> 00:54:05.501
You live your life with
your eyes still open.

824
00:54:05.542 --> 00:54:08.444
And almost nobody
fucking does that anymore.

825
00:54:10.114 --> 00:54:14.484
I'm so sick of trying to
fix my parents' mistakes.

826
00:54:15.119 --> 00:54:17.247
We didn't fuck this
planet up. they did.

827
00:54:17.321 --> 00:54:19.347
Why should we have to fix it?

828
00:54:20.224 --> 00:54:21.692
Let them go. Joanie.

829
00:54:21.892 --> 00:54:22.951
Let them all go.

830
00:54:23.026 --> 00:54:25.325
You don't owe your
life to any of them.

831
00:54:38.142 --> 00:54:39.142
Okay.

832
00:54:40.544 --> 00:54:42.308
Wait. what? Really?

833
00:54:42.379 --> 00:54:44.507
That speech. that speech worked?

834
00:54:45.382 --> 00:54:46.577
Car's out of gas.

835
