842
00:55:29.393 --> 00:55:30.486
Oh. God.

843
00:55:30.861 --> 00:55:31.726
Are you married. too?

844
00:55:31.795 --> 00:55:35.061
No. But. um...

845
00:55:36.533 --> 00:55:39.093
My full name is
Eddie James Ullah.

846
00:55:40.671 --> 00:55:42.196
Does that mean anything to you?

847
00:55:42.272 --> 00:55:43.740
- Should it?
- No.

848
00:55:43.807 --> 00:55:46.106
No. not necessarily.

849
00:55:46.944 --> 00:55:49.914
It's just that my
father was sort of...

850
00:55:51.315 --> 00:55:53.216
loosely affiliated
with your mother.

851
00:55:55.185 --> 00:55:56.185
What?

852
00:55:57.754 --> 00:56:00.724
Alison's second
husband Noah Solloway...

853
00:56:00.924 --> 00:56:04.452
his first wife was a woman
named Helen Solloway.

854
00:56:04.862 --> 00:56:08.560
And after they divorced.
she met my father.

855
00:56:09.433 --> 00:56:10.924
Your mother is Helen Solloway?

856
00:56:11.001 --> 00:56:12.401
Uh. no.

857
00:56:12.669 --> 00:56:14.865
Um. my mother's name is Sierra.

858
00:56:14.938 --> 00:56:16.236
My father's name was Vik.

859
00:56:16.306 --> 00:56:18.537
They had an affair
when he was with Helen.

860
00:56:18.809 --> 00:56:21.677
and that's where I come from.

861
00:56:22.913 --> 00:56:25.610
- Are we related?
- What? No. no. no.

862
00:56:25.682 --> 00:56:27.810
- Are you sure?
- Yes. No way.

863
00:56:28.218 --> 00:56:29.914
My mother is your mother's

864
