here when I was in college.

903
00:58:14.391 --> 00:58:16.758
I even helped restore the
Lobster Roll when Noah bought it.

904
00:58:16.827 --> 00:58:18.171
- so you're not the only person...
- Wait. what?

905
00:58:18.195 --> 00:58:19.823
Who this town
means something to.

906
00:58:19.896 --> 00:58:21.728
And. yeah. yeah. I don't know.

907
00:58:21.798 --> 00:58:26.361
Maybe I was attracted to you
because we shared a certain history.

908
00:58:27.037 --> 00:58:29.082
Because I thought you might
be able to understand my pain.

909
00:58:29.106 --> 00:58:30.583
and I might be able
to understand yours.

910
00:58:30.607 --> 00:58:31.939
Is that such a crime?

911
00:58:33.310 --> 00:58:34.487
- No.
- And I wanted to tell you.

912
00:58:34.511 --> 00:58:36.104
