dealing with so much trauma.

914
00:58:39.316 --> 00:58:41.615
you didn't really let me
get a word in edgewise.

915
00:58:42.652 --> 00:58:43.652
You're right.

916
00:58:53.230 --> 00:58:55.392
So...

917
00:58:57.367 --> 00:58:58.367
Okay.

918
00:59:00.804 --> 00:59:03.273
