923
00:59:14.384 --> 00:59:16.148
Yes. you will.

924
00:59:17.454 --> 00:59:21.289
Maybe not today. maybe not tomorrow.
but soon and for the rest of your life.

925
00:59:22.692 --> 00:59:25.560
- So you have seen a movie.
- It was my mother's favorite film.

926
00:59:25.796 --> 00:59:27.321
Why am I not surprised?

927
00:59:37.641 --> 00:59:39.681
So. what. you're just gonna
go back to your husband?

928
00:59:42.379 --> 00:59:43.870
No. I don't think so.

929
00:59:45.749 --> 00:59:47.411
So where the hell will you go?

930
00:59:48.618 --> 00:59:49.642
I don't know.

931
00:59:54.891 --> 00:59:57.292
Your mother and Helen
were really friends?

932
00:59:59.162 --> 01:00:00.162
Good friends.

933
01:00:01.798 --> 01:00:03.096
So it's possible.

934
01:00:04.101 --> 01:00:05.160
What's possible?

935
01:00:06.870 --> 01:00:08.304
To do things differently.

936
01:00:12.509 --> 01:00:15.274
Can I at least give
you a lift somewhere?

937
01:00:19.583 --> 01:00:20.949
