950
01:01:43.867 --> 01:01:45.893
That he tried to save
her and he couldn't.

951
01:01:47.003 --> 01:01:48.603
And that we were
better off without her.

952
01:01:50.140 --> 01:01:52.439
Oh. wow. That breaks my heart.

953
